               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="206v">1v-206v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s39IHA">قران, Second half (ǧuz’ 16-30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم اقترب للناس حسابهم وهم فى غفلة معرضون</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#206v">-206v</locus>سورة التكاثر مكية ثمان آيات بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم</explicit>
                     <note>Fragmented second half of al-Qur’ān bound in mixed up order. Fols 27r-28r, 42r and 55v are blank. Some fols bound upside down. The text begins with sūra 21 on fol. 1v. Fol. 206v ends with the heading of sura 102. Heading of sura 114 on fol. 204v, text of the sūra on fol. 204r. Different hands. Most sūra titles missing. On some fols red verse markers and sūra titles in red. Endings and beginnings of the lines invisible due to tight binding. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="175r" to="183v">175r-183v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="acephalous apodous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0543IHA">قصيدة الهمزية في مدح خير البرية</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#175r">-175r</locus>محا نوره الظل وقد اثبتت الظلال الضحاء</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#183v">-183v</locus>نقضوا مبرام الصحيفة اذ شدت عليه من العد الانداء</explicit>
                     <note>The folios are bound in wrong order. Vocalized.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
